[[File:Scissors.jpg|thumb|right|250px|[[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]] uses scissors and a [[scalpel]] to bandage [[Nak Pitareeze]]'s leg.]]
'''Scissors''' were a hand-held tool made of two blades used to cut thin materials, such as hair. '''Pruning scissors''' were used to trim or sculpt plants and bushes.

[[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]] used scissors to cut a bandage for [[Nak Pitareeze]] after he was injured in a crash-landing on [[Kalarba/Legends|Kalarba]].

